headline: The Great Rotation Has Started—and Maybe Ended. What to Do Next.
summary: Suddenly, tech stocks are struggling and a variety of out-of-favor sectors--value, small-caps, overseas, dividends, manufacturing—are hot. Why trying to do everything at once is so difficult.
